  id: pkg_aur
  displayName: AUR
  slot: 1
  rarity: 4
  description: start each TURN with a generated C/Rust card. on Arch, any rarity and costs 1 less this turn; off-distro, common only with no discount.
  flavourText: probably maintained by one person and a shell script named pls-work.sh.
  designNotes: Arch 4-star Runtime package. Scope TURN. On Arch: generate random C/Rust card up to Legendary rarity and apply -1 temporary cost. Off-distro: generate Common C/Rust only with no discount. Uses existing generated-card pool; requiresSystem card-generation if no eligible pool is available. Runtime slot intentionally does not conflict with systemd Daemon.
  intendedDistroId: arch
  requiresSystem:
  - card-generation
